name: rttys
description: Access your terminal from anywhere via the web.
full_description:
# [Rttys](https://github.com/zhaojh329/rttys)
## Shows a list of commands or help for one command

    sudo docker run -it zhaojh329/rttys:latest -h
    sudo docker run -it zhaojh329/rttys:latest run -h

## Simple run

    sudo docker run -it -p 5912:5912 -p 5913:5913 zhaojh329/rttys:latest
